>> source: https://www.mybakingaddiction.com/beer-bread
>> yield: 1 loaf
>> prep time: 5 minutes
>> cook time: 55 minutes

Preheat #oven at 190c{}.
@Butter{2%tbsp} a #20x10 cm loaf pan{} and set aside.
In a large bowl, combine the @flour{400%g}, @sugar{80%g}, @salt{1%tsp} and @beer{350%ml}. Mix well.
Pour into the loaf pan and bake for ~{55%minutes}.
